title: Future I cut short
body:
それが頂点の
務めならば…！

ならば

俺が摘んだ
未来は？

今更許せと
言うつもりはない

Sore ga Chōten no Tsutomenaraba…!
Naraba
Ore ga tsunda Mirai wa?
Imasara yuruse to
iutsumori wanai

whats the actual translation of this?

blog.description: A roleplaying group for Boku No Hero Academia based out of Tumblr! You can apply by clicking Here!

summary: About us  |  Taken Characters List  |  Muse Page  |  Application Hello! BNHA-Logged is looking for new members! We’re a Roleplay...
caption:
About us  |  Taken Characters List  |  Muse Page  |  Application

Hello! BNHA-Logged is looking for new members! We’re a Roleplay group for Boku No Hero Academia/My Hero Academia based here on Tumblr. If you’re interested in roleplaying BNHA with a friendly group, open to all levels of rp experience as long as you can be active and are willing to learn. Open to minors and adults, all of our rps are sfw/minor friendly! We do have an invite-only discord group where we convene to discuss the rp but all of the actual rp is on Tumblr.

Please check our taken characters list before applying, we do not allow doubles! We ask that whatever character you decide to take, you do not contradict canon. However, your personal headcanons for them are acceptable as long as it keeps to canon.

A few characters we have available that we really need are: Shigaraki Tomura, Mina Ashido, Mirio Togata, Hawks, Nejire Hadou, Midnight, Mr. Compress, Hatsume Mei
